        <abstract> 
<p>Accepts CD’s proposal for new revised edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>; will pay $50 [dollars or pounds!?] for casts of the plates and pay CD on sales.</p>  
<p>Appleton edition of CD’s <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi> [1871] still selling well.</p>  
<p>Also wants plates sent with CD’s new work on <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>. CD should arrange this with Murray’s.</p> 
        </abstract>
